description: Jake is a bartender and keeps in shape by going to the gym every day of the week. He's an interesting guy-- he's got some really cool stories to tell about the people that he meets at the bar he works at.When he's not working and not at the gym, you can find him at home on the couch watching one of his hundreds of DVDs or cuddled up on the couch with his girlfriend. Lucky girl.
title: Jake
